I met Kevin @kevinrudolf years ago, when our paths kept crossing at radio shows that he was headlining when “Let It Rock” w/ Lil Wayne @liltunechi was one of the biggest songs in the world. Well, it’s about to be again, with a new reimagined version, in a way that feels like it was always meant to be…as an awesome collaboration with the amazing rising talent @bvrnoutofficial Kevin has always been an incredible undefined artist, writer and producer that you can’t put in a box (as all the greats are) with his roots in electronic music. Can’t wait for you all to hear this! Out December 1, on @totalsmash

The @vavomusic 🤠🤠 show was a movie last night at @mulcahyspub on Long Island. It’s been quite a ride seeing my boys @aldenmartin_ @jessevavo @maxwkessler start from a chance meeting on @soundcloud to selling out shows with thousands of screaming fans. Not only are the insanely talented, but also the most humble and kind guys I know. Couldn’t be happier or more proud to call them my brothers. Thanks to everyone for coming out last night and to all the Day 1’s for supporting. Wait until you see what’s about to pop off in 2024 🚀 💥 #YEEDM is here baby 🤠 Special thanks to @laidbackluke & @partypupils for coming out to support as well. ❤️
